        What Brisbane Sellers Need to Know When Dealing with a Buyer's Agent
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Buyer's agents are increasingly common in Brisbane's inner east. Here is how they work, how they change negotiation dynamics, and what sellers should understand before accepting an offer.
      </p>
